            <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">BEDFORD</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">N.H.</ENAMEX>--I caught up with <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Bill Bradley</ENAMEX> here <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">today</TIMEX>, having not seen him
